{"tid":1445763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰前往瑪嘉烈醫院探望燒傷同事","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:28.000Z","uid":212626,"like":30,"dislike":587,"uniUserReply":159,"replies":[{"pid":"3db383d9f1db5ca09401177baafe7a36b1318365","tid":1445763,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"警務處處長探望燒傷同事<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  警務處處長盧偉聰今日（八月十一日）晚上，到瑪嘉烈醫院探望今日較早前，在尖沙咀警署內執勤時被暴徒投擲汽油彈引致雙腳燒傷的一名同事。對於有同事因為執勤時受到嚴重傷害，處長感到非常難過。<br />\n   <br />\n  對於暴徒罔顧他人安全的非法暴力行為，處長感到非常憤慨，並予以最強烈譴責。針對任何引致他人身體嚴重受傷、甚至威脅生命安全的暴力行為，警隊必定全力追究。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月11日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時12分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/11/P2019081100825.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F11%2FP2019081100825.htm&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16RYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=3f95804f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/11/P2019081100825.htm</a>"},{"pid":"561328224989d9e8abd223b760ca939f62bef9e1","tid":1445763,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf52cdb35623f7981a2c8a0fb333a37de89faf7","tid":1445763,"uid":62891,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:30:04.000Z","msg":"食屎啦"},{"pid":"56c90f8bd4be1ab9c3a81d3933539c4427e3f5ec","tid":1445763,"uid":244034,"like":191,"dislike":2,"score":189,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你自己啲夥計做嘅"},{"pid":"9fcd4f0a209598177b42a75c031bacc7f8e74384","tid":1445763,"uid":37197,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"大家都係做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a641d8f9438f6563630f52b1a1bc7070d5e23f","tid":1445763,"uid":68738,"like":16,"disl